Hotfix 0.2.2
 - pytc -b was incorrectly fetching the home timeline rather than
   the public timeline.
 - In usage, the default timeline was incorrectly labelled public
   instead of home.

Hotfix 0.2.1
 - Fixed pytc <count> to specify how many tweets to retrieve.

Release 0.2
 - Switched to tweepy library.

Release 0.1
 - Initial version. Supports tweeting, searching, reading other's 
   timelines, the public timeline, some basic info about users, 
   and @replies.
